    Bullet

    The Enemy class represents an enemy in the game.

    The Enemyspawn class is responsible for managing the spawning of enemies in the game.
    GameOverScreen
    GameOverScreen is displayed when the game ends.
    GameScreen
    GameScreen class represents the main game screen where the player controls a spaceship, fights enemies, and manages the game state.
    LeaderboardScreen
    LeaderboardScreen displays the leaderboard entries from a file.
    MenuScreen
    MenuScreen is the initial screen of the game.
